data.description: Come see this fantastic 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a flat lot located in a great neighborhood with wide streets and close to downtown. Walk up to the cute front porch and go inside to a welcoming area. There is a large dining room with tons of natural light and gleaming original hardwood floors. The kitchen has been updated with a beautiful granite countertops, tile and stainless appliances.  The den has a great wood-burning fireplace (gas hook up right there if you would rather) and brand new sliding doors that take you out to a great outdoor area which is perfect for entertaining! The deck overlooks the flat, fenced back yard and there is also a great porch for more space to hang out.  Your will love this home from the moment you arrive!
